Usage: delete_cell_obs [-help] -cells <libCell/ptnCell|topCell|vCell>+ {-obs_shapes <shape>+ | [[-rects {{llx1 lly1 urx1 ury1} {llx2 lly2 urx2 ury2}...}> | -polygon { <x1 y1> <x2 y2> <x3 y3> ...}] -layers <layer>+]}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-cells <libCell/ptnCell|topCell|vCell>+    # Cell name or pointer.
                                           # ((libCell/ptnCell|topCell|vCell)+, required)
-layers <layer>+          # Layer name or pointer ((layer)+, optional)
-obs_shapes <shape>+      # Specifies the cell obstruction shape pointers.
                          # ((shape)+, optional)
-polygon { <x1 y1> <x2 y2> <x3 y3> ...}    # Obs polygon.
                                           # (point_list, optional)
-rects {{llx1 lly1 urx1 ury1} {llx2 lly2 urx2 ury2}...}>
                          # obs rect lists (box_list, optional)